Cell["\<\
EulerRotationMatrix::usage =
\t\"EulerRotationMatrix[{\[Alpha],\[Beta],\[Gamma]}] gives the 3D rotation \
matrix for the rotation product Rz(\[Alpha])Ry(\[Beta])Rz(\[Gamma]). See VMK \
p30.\";
\t\
\>", "Input",
